panels.name: Top Ingest Spikes for Top 5 Sources Per Day
panels.queryString:
_index=sumologic_volume sizeInBytes 
| where _sourceCategory="source_volume"
| parse regex "\"(?<source>[^\"]+)\"\:\{\"sizeInBytes\"\:(?<bytes>\d+),\"count\"\:(?<count>\d+)\}" multi
| timeslice 1d
| bytes/1024/1024/1024 as gbytes 
| sum(gbytes) as gbytes by _timeslice, source
| compare with timeshift 1d
| sort _timeslice desc, gbytes desc
| 1 as rownum
| accum rownum by _timeslice
| where _accum <= 5 // limit by this
| fields _timeslice, gbytes, gbytes_1d, source
| if (!(isNull(gbytes_1d)), ((gbytes - gbytes_1d) / gbytes_1d) * 100, gbytes * 100) as percent_diff
| if (isNull(gbytes_1d), 0, gbytes_1d) as gbytes_1d
| where percent_diff > 0
| sort percent_diff
| limit 25
| fields _timeslice, source, percent_diff, gbytes, gbytes_1d
